66
00:03:54,760 --> 00:03:56,040
That makes sense.

67
00:03:56,200 --> 00:03:57,000
Miss Shi Yi,

68
00:03:57,000 --> 00:03:57,760
may I know what is

69
00:03:57,920 --> 00:03:58,680
