131
00:06:17,920 --> 00:06:18,560
I will go to

132
00:06:18,680 --> 00:06:20,040
the recording studio this afternoon.

133
00:06:20,160 --> 00:06:21,040
And I happen to pass by

134
00:06:21,040 --> 00:06:21,840
your institute,

135
00:06:22,000 --> 00:06:23,360
