136
00:06:24,440 --> 00:06:25,920
What, are you not happy to see me?

137
00:06:26,440 --> 00:06:27,560
Of course I am happy.

138
00:06:28,880 --> 00:06:29,480
Hi, Miss Shi.

139
00:06:29,720 --> 00:06:30,760
-Hello, Miss Shi.
-Miss Shi.

140
00:06:31,159 --> 00:06:31,800
You guys continue.

141
