155
00:06:59,120 --> 00:07:00,320
Wait for me then.

156
00:07:00,480 --> 00:07:01,560
I will go get ready.

157
00:07:34,880 --> 00:07:35,840
I'll head up then.

158
00:07:36,000 --> 00:07:36,600
You go park the car.

159
00:07:36,860 --> 00:07:37,220
Okay.

160
00:07:39,340 --> 00:07:39,740
Wait.

161
00:07:44,270 --> 00:07:45,060
You can lecture,

162
00:07:45,360 --> 00:07:46,700
