169
00:08:02,080 --> 00:08:02,480
Go on then.

170
00:08:03,720 --> 00:08:04,200
See you.

171
00:08:12,760 --> 00:08:13,600
What do you want for dinner?

172
00:08:13,600 --> 00:08:14,520
I don't know, what do you want to eat?

173
00:08:14,520 --> 00:08:15,720
The class today was so interesting,

174
00:08:15,720 --> 00:08:16,520
-right?
-Yeah.

175
00:08:17,400 --> 00:08:18,760
Miss Shi.

176
00:08:19,040 --> 00:08:19,800
Is that you?

177
00:08:20,040 --> 00:08:20,800
I am from the winter vacation class.

178
00:08:20,960 --> 00:08:22,200
Last year's winter vacation class.

179
00:08:23,720 --> 00:08:24,280
Lin Jia?

180
00:08:24,440 --> 00:08:25,280
Yeah, that's me.

181
00:08:25,440 --> 00:08:26,720
You still remember me?

182
00:08:26,799 --> 00:08:28,280
Shi Yi, are you Shi Yi?

183
00:08:29,200 --> 00:08:30,039
I watched your drama.

184
00:08:30,880 --> 00:08:32,480
You are even involved in plays now?

185
00:08:32,640 --> 00:08:33,840
I am about to graduate,

186
00:08:34,000 --> 00:08:34,320
so I am too busy

187
00:08:34,400 --> 00:08:35,720
to follow you.

188
00:08:35,840 --> 00:08:37,440
That was a rare occasion. I was doing my friend a favor.

189
00:08:37,720 --> 00:08:38,200
Miss Shi.

190
00:08:38,320 --> 00:08:39,360
Can I get your autograph?

191
00:08:39,520 --> 00:08:39,920
Sure.

192
00:08:40,240 --> 00:08:40,800
Thank you.

193
00:08:40,920 --> 00:08:41,840
Can I write the name of the drama?

194
00:08:41,960 --> 00:08:42,200
Absolutely.

195
00:08:42,200 --> 00:08:43,720
There is no notice about a big shot coming.

196
