At least let us hear the end.

199
00:08:47,360 --> 00:08:48,840
Miss Shi, you are so talented.

200
00:08:49,160 --> 00:08:49,760
Miss Shi, please sign your name here.

201
00:08:49,880 --> 00:08:50,160
Okay.

202
00:08:50,280 --> 00:08:51,320
Miss Shi, you are amazing.

203
00:08:51,560 --> 00:08:52,960
-Miss Shi, please give me your autograph.
-Thank you.

204
