00:08:55,280 --> 00:08:55,760
Miss Shi, me as well.

207
00:08:56,040 --> 00:08:57,840
Miss Shi, can I have your autograph?

208
00:08:58,080 --> 00:08:59,080
That's it, everybody.

209
00:08:59,280 --> 00:09:00,080
That's the end of today's lecture.

210
00:09:00,240 --> 00:09:01,120
Thank you.

211
00:09:03,920 --> 00:09:04,600
Professor.

212
00:09:05,080 --> 00:09:05,800
