no time reserved for questions.

218
00:09:13,400 --> 00:09:14,640
Besides,

219
00:09:15,940 --> 00:09:17,300
my wife has been waiting for me downstairs

220
00:09:17,340 --> 00:09:18,270
for a long time.

221
00:09:20,160 --> 00:09:21,000
Your wife?

222
00:09:21,090 --> 00:09:22,330
