236
00:09:47,000 --> 00:09:48,600
That's so admirable.

237
00:09:48,760 --> 00:09:49,160
Yeah.

238
00:09:49,360 --> 00:09:51,200
Professor, there's no need to answer questions.

239
00:09:51,440 --> 00:09:53,320
