240
00:09:53,600 --> 00:09:54,800
Exactly, exactly.

241
00:09:54,960 --> 00:09:55,880
Let's talk about that.

242
00:09:57,920 --> 00:10:00,440
All right, from now on,

243
00:10:00,600 --> 00:10:01,400
everyone

244
00:10:01,640 --> 00:10:02,480
