247
00:10:07,800 --> 00:10:09,440
Professor, I have a question.

248
00:10:10,440 --> 00:10:11,560
Professor, you said

249
00:10:11,760 --> 00:10:13,760
Venus was rather unpopular

250
00:10:13,870 --> 00:10:14,840
in terms of planetary research.

251
00:10:15,040 --> 00:10:15,640
Then why

252
00:10:15,800 --> 00:10:16,760
did you choose it?

253
00:10:20,450 --> 00:10:21,720
Venus to me,

254
00:10:21,820 --> 00:10:22,990
is the future of earth.

255
00:10:23,600 --> 00:10:24,650
I want to see the future.

256
00:10:26,400 --> 00:10:28,520
What turned a planet

257
00:10:28,760 --> 00:10:30,520
that was once livable,

258
00:10:30,960 --> 00:10:32,200
with all kinds of species,

259
00:10:32,400 --> 00:10:33,640
into this planet

260
00:10:33,840 --> 00:10:36,000
that has an uncontrolled greenhouse effect.

261
00:10:36,960 --> 00:10:38,120
In fact, by studying Venus,

262
00:10:38,190 --> 00:10:39,320
we better understand

263
00:10:39,520 --> 00:10:40,840
how to protect our own planet.

264
00:10:41,640 --> 00:10:42,280
Of course.

265
00:10:43,000 --> 00:10:44,760
I also wish that human beings, in the future,

266
00:10:45,080 --> 00:10:46,600
could transform Venus

267
00:10:46,640 --> 00:10:47,840
into our second home.

268
00:10:48,520 --> 00:10:49,240
Professor,

269
00:10:49,640 --> 00:10:50,380
the surface temperature of Venus

270
00:10:50,440 --> 00:10:51,680
can reach up to 500 degrees.

271
00:10:52,080 --> 00:10:54,080
Wouldn't it be too difficult to live there?

272
00:10:54,500 --> 00:10:55,240
Yeah.

273
00:10:55,520 --> 00:10:57,370
Yeah, it is indeed very hard.

274
00:10:58,000 --> 00:11:00,480
High levels of radiation and corrosive acid rain

275
00:11:00,840 --> 00:11:01,440
are no doubt

276
00:11:01,600 --> 00:11:02,400
great challenges.

277
00:11:03,360 --> 00:11:04,960
But our scientists

278
00:11:05,120 --> 00:11:06,440
have never given up.

279
00:11:06,800 --> 00:11:08,360
Since last century,

280
00:11:08,600 --> 00:11:09,080
they have proposed

281
00:11:09,160 --> 00:11:10,280
all kinds of solutions.

282
00:11:10,560 --> 00:11:12,360
Such as building a sun shield

283
00:11:12,560 --> 00:11:13,440
above its atmosphere

284
00:11:13,560 --> 00:11:14,480
to improve its environment.

285
00:11:15,080 --> 00:11:17,120
Or, to build a city above the clouds.

286
00:11:18,200 --> 00:11:19,160
It's just that

287
00:11:19,320 --> 00:11:20,320
implementing these ideas

288
00:11:20,480 --> 00:11:21,640
would be really hard.

289
00:11:22,560 --> 00:11:24,000
But anything is possible.

290
00:11:24,560 --> 00:11:25,680
As long as we persist

291
00:11:25,840 --> 00:11:26,480
long enough,

292
00:11:26,880 --> 00:11:28,080
every impossibility

293
00:11:28,280 --> 00:11:29,920
