679
00:30:22,760 --> 00:30:23,600
It's called a drying room.

680
00:30:24,600 --> 00:30:24,920
When I was a kid,

681
00:30:25,040 --> 00:30:26,560
my grandfather gave me one Guqin,

682
00:30:26,680 --> 00:30:28,400
which was said to be from someone famous.

683
00:30:28,520 --> 00:30:29,920
The manufacturing process takes two years,

684
00:30:30,040 --> 00:30:31,320
