685
00:30:31,840 --> 00:30:32,760
is spent to dry in a room.

686
00:30:33,560 --> 00:30:35,040
Like these ones here,

687
00:30:35,240 --> 00:30:36,840
waiting to see the outside world.

688
00:30:39,120 --> 00:30:39,960
Now that I think about it,

689
00:30:40,120 --> 00:30:40,600
our ancestors

690
00:30:40,760 --> 00:30:41,880
have left us many things

691
00:30:42,160 --> 00:30:42,760
