693
00:30:44,400 --> 00:30:46,520
Not just for the people, but the stuff as well.

694
00:30:47,200 --> 00:30:48,320
We have to endure loneliness

695
00:30:48,520 --> 00:30:49,600
and hardship

696
00:30:49,720 --> 00:30:50,700
until we finally achieve greatness.

697
00:30:52,600 --> 00:30:53,920
Miss Shi sure can

698
